Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------text-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎麼的就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 你看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誒? 這不是我們新婚那次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我整理抽屜的時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好年輕! 話說那時我真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的 你現在也很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,和小愛結婚 我每天都像是做夢一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,修吾你真會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,修吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,修吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,社團那邊你已經引退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上有畢業相冊製作委員會議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們剛才看到姐姐的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.32,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「ゆいっちんぐ」->「まいっちんぐ」,出自「まいっちんぐマチコ先生」:「討厭啦!真知子老師」,\N原作漫畫最早於1980年開始連載。
Comment: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,「動畫沉寂會」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,臉很奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然很快又變回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪是怎麼個奇怪法?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 就像以前的動畫人物一樣臉變扁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看來未乃愛你是太疲憊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟學園祭之後發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我啊 我說的是真…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小…小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我說那兩個人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你很沒禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡奇怪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你問哪裡? 看了還不明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,第一節是美術課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該換教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛這邊是有什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什麼黑暗的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑而幽暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,吞噬一切的地獄…地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那地獄一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,振作一點啊 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,之前是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我一走到這邊…
Comment: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是吃了什麼奇怪的東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛正看到一些我們看不見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要去保健室?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,誒? 剛才就在這的啊
Comment: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛 午飯你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,便當? 還是去買麵包?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的午間套餐B有炸雞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那還真是讓人難以割捨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛 午休的時候有部會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,課一下子就上完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,從第一節課開始到現在也就過了一分多鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是喝點東西冷靜一下吧 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,女僕?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就交給塞巴斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她說話了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請享用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fe0}S'il vous pla{\fnFOT-Skip Std D\fs40}î{\fs35\fn方正正准黑_GBK}t
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯 做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的動作很精彩呢 塞巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要加入田徑部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這個能給我一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那老師我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛閃閃發光!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,確實不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,以往這時塞巴斯都會沏一杯格雷伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而這卻是焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是那裡不對勁嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,關於明年部長的人選…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不覺得奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所有社團都開始討論換屆的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍的一切都在變得不正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛一大早開始就是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪? 你覺得什麼奇怪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你那邊就很奇怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛是不是看到了些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也終於擁有了邪眼的力…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍一切都很奇怪 你們注意不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或許有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說是有點感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是動畫的總編劇換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,總編劇?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 都已經這麼多集了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是田廣溜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.46,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「田広」->「広田光毅」:「廣田光毅」,該作的總編劇。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過是那個傢伙被替換了 會有這麼大影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看來需要確認一下情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們再看一遍片頭曲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,片頭曲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再看一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒帶了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Comment: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,「動畫沉寂會」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:25.90,op - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何をしてても退屈な every day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.11,op - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}コ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:25.90,op - cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管做什麼 每天都是那麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.11,op - cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是沒什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?不是不是 剛才那是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都這麼平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你冷靜點 未乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,都這個階段了要是我們太動搖 會被11集棄番的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,11集棄番?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因為和至今為止看到的劇情發展不太一樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,觀眾可能會說我們題材不明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我們定位為什麼題材 觀眾才會認可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,日常?校園?萌?少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟動畫題材近年來被細分得越來越複雜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我們要先確定一下是搞笑動漫還是現實動漫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下來就需要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,閃光及衝擊波防護措施!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.52,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「対閃光、対ショック防御」->「対ショック、 対閃光防御」,「宇宙戰艦大和號」中波動炮發射準備環節的一環。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子的是搞笑動漫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,眼…我的眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.62,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「目が、目がぁ～!」,「天空之城」中最後階段希達與巴斯唸出咒語「巴魯斯!」,\N放出強光致使羅穆斯卡大佐短暫失明,大佐喊出的台詞。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是現實動漫的話就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…但是我們卻還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這完全不夠現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要是現實的話會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還能行!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,記得請我吃醋漬青花魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這很現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,確實現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂現實…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正艺黑_GBK\fs70\bord0\b1\frz10.74\pos(602,675)}一同討論、\N盟友光輝背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為我要死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛還不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和貓前輩再聊會天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天反應有點劇烈很奇怪 我有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家反而覺得我是不正常的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝前輩?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,中野前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩曾說過你們家是兄弟六人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,誒…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,最年長的哥哥年紀和你差很遠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,比如差個20歲什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 這樣就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙的兄弟們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才好像是下了陣雨 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,回來得有點晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 「天然女僕」的錄像我們已經看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.20,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「天然メイド」->「少年メイド」:「少年女僕」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小未?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子怎麼了 突然這麼奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們也已經看完「魔法使茉莉」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.55,comment,,0,0,0,,註:「魔法使いモリー」->「魔法使いサリー」:「魔法使莎莉」,接下來的作畫神似魔法使莎莉。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去準備晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,來看看誰先跑到廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:43.91,Default-up,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:44.78,Default-up,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,據說城市裡出現了巨型機械獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,巨型機械獸?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似正在朝這邊走來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,結界已經佈置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 塊塊前輩倒是跟平時沒什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,武藏鏡 塊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,紅蓮射門!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,火力有點太猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都絲毫不感到奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這又不是動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,「又不是動畫」?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼不好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,未乃愛從昨天開始就淨說些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的靈魂到底被什麼東西支配了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,動畫就是動畫 不是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這才叫異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在否定動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.02,comment,,0,0,0,,註:梗「玻璃假面」中月影千草的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,本以為你比任何人都要深愛著動畫研究部…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的孩子!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小有棲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不能接受動畫的方方面面 何談愛著動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你的交情到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼突然就到傍晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你的交情到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你在否定動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小未 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 是我出問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小未…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再忍耐一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很快就要迎來結尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 感覺我在被大家盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你說了討厭動畫是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒說過!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能不要這樣叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 有些東西不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是未乃愛提醒 我可能也注意不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我都開始以為是自己不正常了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是有什麼原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,原因?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,正常來講不該有的事開始發生一定是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,正常來講不該有的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是因為你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,早就覺得奇怪了 貓竟然會說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你到現在才吐槽這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次開門的時候 你出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那時還真是多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然後你就叫我別再打開那扇門了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,中野前輩和其他人在跟你交談後 事情就越變越怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是因為你!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 把一切弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,門…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,全是我的回合!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.11,comment,,0,0,0,,//註:「すべて俺のターン」->「ずっと俺のターン」:一直是我的回合,用來揶揄對方;一說該梗出自「遊戲王」,\N而實際上其出處不明。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,出來吧!黑紅藍黃金色巨龍!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,召喚!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小有棲 小美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,連我也…變成動畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,枷鎖被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,「觀察者」不在的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,平衡已經被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你來自那邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我是來自動畫世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,貓前輩是動畫?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?竟然先吐槽我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界再過不久就要被動畫吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吞噬?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰派來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,新世界大爆炸!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家…
